parameters: \N<Zozoie>Who's there? What do you want with me?
\N<Segi>It's me... Do you remember? I've come to talk to you.

\N<Zozoie>If it isn't the woman from the other day. Talk? What could
you possibly have to discuss with me?
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zozoie>Heh, I can tell by looking in your eyes. You're lying. You
don't have anything to talk about with me, do you? You've
come here to continue what we started last time, haven't
you?

\N<Zozoie>You reek of a female in heat right now. It's proof that
you're wetting your crotch just standing before a male like
me.
\N<Segi>Wh-What are you saying...
\N<Segi>Wha...!?

\N<Zozoie>Surprised? In exchange for behaving myself in this hole,
I've been assured a certain degree of freedom. Otherwise, I
wouldn't be able to fuck any women, right?
\N<Segi>Don't come any closer...

\N<Zozoie>If I don't come closer, how can we continue what we started
last time? That's why you showed up here so willingly, isn't
it?
3_4aa
\N<Segi>Ah...!?
\N<Segi>Mm...ah!? Uh...!
\N<Zozoie>Hehe...!
\N<Segi>Mm...ah!? Uh...!

\N<Zozoie>Haha, look at that. You're already fully prepared on this
side.
\N<Segi>Mm...ah! Ugh...!

\N<Zozoie>Hey, hey, what's wrong? You're shaking, aren't you? I
haven't had a woman in days, so make sure you entertain me
properly, alright?
\N<Segi>Mm...! Stop...ah!

\N<Zozoie>Heh, no one's coming to save you. This is the perfect place
to enjoy continuing what we started last time.

\N<Segi>(Just as I imagined, a greedy and despicable man... I
mustn't lose my composure here. That's exactly what he
wants.)

\N<Segi>(That's right... this might actually be more convenient for
me than I thought.)

\N<Segi>(This man... he's confident in himself. That's why he acts
so crudely and straightforwardly, even though he knows it,
he doesn't restrain himself.)

\N<Segi>(If that's the case... there's only one thing I must do
right now...)
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zozoie>What's wrong? Gone silent. Have you finally decided to let
yourself be fucked by me?

\N<Segi>The strength that a woman like me could never hope to shake
off... You have a robust body.

\N<Zozoie>Oh? What about it? Are you sizing up the man who's about to
take care of you? I've been pent up too, so I'll take you
without reservation.
\N<Segi>Mm...

\N<Zozoie>Hehe, nice. Looks like you've finally realized that
resistance is futile.

\N<Segi>The other day... I saw your battle. It was very intense and
stimulating... Your strength was the only thing that stood
out.

\N<Zozoie>Heh, is that so? You were watching that? Seeing a
stimulating man like me made you wet yourself, huh? And you
couldn't hold back anymore so you came here?
\N<Segi>That might be... yes, that might be it...
\N<Segi>Mm...

\N<Zozoie>Heh, if that's the case, there's no need for modesty, right?
Come on, strip. Or do you want me to strip you?
\N<Segi>...I have a husband whom I love.

\N<Zozoie>What's this all of a sudden? What about him? Don't tell me
you're trying to stay chaste for your husband?

\N<Segi>Perhaps that's part of it. However, right now, my husband is
imprisoned in this place.
\N<Zozoie>...And?

\N<Segi>There's no hope for his release. In other words... the
chances of him returning to me and our son are extremely
slim.

\N<Segi>That's why I'm hesitating now. Whether I can continue to
love my husband who remains imprisoned...
\N<Zozoie>...

\N<Segi>That's why... before I give myself to you, I want you to
give me the resolve I need to push myself forward.

\N<Zozoie>I see... You want the resolve to switch from your weak
husband to a man like me, huh?

\N<Segi>Yes... That's why I want to hear about your strength from
your own lips.

\N<Segi>If I am convinced that you are a strong man... then I can
entrust myself to you with peace of mind.

\N<Zozoie>Hmph... Fine. I don't know what you're up to, but I guess I
can tell you?

\N<Zozoie>After all... without that inhibiting drug or whatever the
Luda guys have, it wouldn't even be a conversation.
\N<Segi>...

\N<Zozoie>But it's not for any significant reason. You see, I was a
test subject for some drug made by those Luda guys.
\N<Segi>Mind. Luda... right.

\N<Zozoie>Yeah, that was the name. A drug aimed at regenerating
subcutaneous tissue damage... was it?

\N<Zozoie>It was touted as something that could be repurposed for
wartime use. Apparently, it could turn soldiers more
aggressive? Well, I must say, I think it worked on me.

\N<Zozoie>When did they start mass production? That's about when I
escaped from Luda's experiments.

\N<Zozoie>After that, I drifted from place to place. Heh, of course,
I've done plenty of things I can't tell people about.
\N<Segi>And after being captured by Luda... that brings us to now.
\N<Zozoie>Yeah, something like that. Satisfied?
\N<Segi>...Yes, very much so.
\N<Luda Soldier>Hey, you. What are you doing?

\N<Zozoie>Tch... Just when things were getting good. You're such a
dutiful lapdog.
\N<Luda Soldier>Watch your language. I'm asking what you're doing there.
\N<Zozoie>Nothing? This woman came onto me, no lie.
\N<Luda Soldier>What did you say?

\N<Segi>...Don't talk nonsense. There's no way I would do such a
thing.

\N<Segi>Soldier. Who will you believe, the ramblings of a common
citizen or a vicious death row inmate?
\N<Zozoie>Woman... what are you trying to pull?
\N<Segi>Well... what am I trying to do indeed.

\N<Segi>There will be no further discussion with you. If the
opportunity arises, let's meet again.
